<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Modern Web Experience</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
  
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #2c3e50;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #1e88e5;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
  
    p {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #37474f;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease;
      border-left: 6px solid #42a5f5;
    }
  
    p:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
  
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
  
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e88e5, #42a5f5);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
  
    header nav a {
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      position: relative;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    header nav a:hover {
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }
  
    header nav a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 50%;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: #ffeb3b;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    header nav a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
      left: 0;
    }
  
    button {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #42a5f5, #1e88e5);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
  
    button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #1e88e5, #42a5f5);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
      background: #1e88e5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 -6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
  
    footer:hover {
      background: #42a5f5;
    }
  </style>
  
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('head') %>

  <h1>Welcome to Our Modern Web App</h1>
  <p>
    Explore our platform to discover cutting-edge solutions and tools for your digital needs. 
    Built with a robust backend powered by Node.js and Express, combined with MongoDB for seamless data management.
  </p>

  <p>
    Experience the latest trends in responsive design and user-friendly interfaces. 
    Join us as we redefine the standards of web development with modern technologies and intuitive designs.
  </p>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Modern Web Experience. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
